Pair your Bang & Olufsen Cisco 980 to a Bluetooth device
Put your headset into pairing mode to make it discoverable to other devices.
Your Bang & Olufsen Cisco 980 can save up to eight different BluetoothÂ® devices and maintain simultaneous connections with up to two devices at once.
To get the most out of your headset, download and set up the Bang & Olufsen app on your mobile device.
1
Press and hold the Bluetooth button on the bottom of the right ear cup for two seconds.
2
Enable Bluetooth on your device.
You can enable and disable Bluetooth from the Settings menu on most call devices.
3
Select your headset from the device list.
By default, your headset will appear in the device list as Bang & Olufsen Cisco 980.